      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEY BARBIE GIRL (5) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (18.31) at this track in a Maiden over 320m. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Looks the one to beat. CLASSIC LASS (8) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden after seven starts. Was in the placings again last time finishing second (18.47) at this track. Will give a great sight again. CREEPING CLOVER (2) was a strong course and distance winner last time, claiming a Maiden in a powerful 18.58 and a new PB here. Expected to feature again. NO EYE CONTACT (1) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
